Versions 523 And Later Are Broken And Cannot Use Flow Or Download Messages):

For anyone who doesn’t know how to sideload Facebook Messenger with the Flow tweak on iOS (note: versions 523 and later are broken and cannot use Flow or download messages):
If you already have an Apple certificate and use Feather, you won’t be able to install on iOS 26 anymore — switch to ZSign ( its interface is much better than Feather.
After importing your certificate, use the Flow IPA version 515 — this build supports downloading encrypted messages and enables message preview (without being prompted to update to view messages).
That’s all for now.
